    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_237_18",
    "text": "为响应我校“知体育健体魄强精神”主 题活动，提高学生的身体素质，锻炼体能，特 提出以下倡议：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.515478761699064,
      0.3210662591790823,
      0.9229661627069834,
      0.38864128358589073
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_237",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_237_6",
    "text": "1．萌欲通过阅读下列语段来加深对体育内 涵的理解，但遇到了一些小问题，请你帮她 解决。(6分)",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.06383489320854331,
      0.3365168300861666,
      0.48596112311015116,
      0.40561993293433507
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_237",
    "order": 12
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_237_19",
    "text": "①充分利用学校健身场地，积极参加课 内外体育锻炼，如踢足球、跳绳等。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5173986081113511,
      0.3945838108578463,
      0.9229661627069834,
      0.4387282991638015
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_237",
    "order": 13
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_237_7",
    "text": "体育，是一种以身体与智力活动为基 本手段，根据人体生长发育、技能形成和机 能提高等规律，达到促进全面发育、 身体素质与全面教育水平 体质 与提高运动能力 生活方式与提 高生活质量的一种有意识、有目的、有组织 的社会活动。体育包括体育文化、体育教 育、体育活动、体育竞赛、体育设施、体育组 织、体育科学技术等诸多要素。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.09071274298056156,
      0.41020416825841505,
      0.4888408927285817,
      0.6270215204380492
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_237",
    "order": 14
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_237_20",
    "text": "②每天坚持跑步运动，完成以班级为单 位的集体跑步任务。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5159587233021359,
      0.44416146695530373,
      0.9217662586993041,
      0.48796638227429007
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_237",
    "order": 15
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_237_21",
    "text": "③节假日期间坚持每天锻炼一小时，积 极参加户外运动，养成科学锻炼的习惯。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5159587233021359,
      0.4932297635723078,
      0.9232061435085194,
      0.5394116898000764
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_237",
    "order": 16
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_237_22",
    "text": "雏燕展翅竞飞跃， _。同学 们，让我们一起走到阳光下，去感受体育的 魅力，享受运动的快乐！",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5147588192944564,
      0.5429772061632497,
      0.9227261819054475,
      0.6122500955049026
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_237",
    "order": 17
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_237_23",
    "text": "2023年4月13日 倡议人：校宣传委",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.7556995440364771,
      0.618192622776858,
      0.9217662586993041,
      0.6619975380958445
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_237",
    "order": 18
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_237_8",
    "text": "身体教育和知识教育之间必须保持平 héng( )。体育应造就体格健壮的勇 士，并且使健全的精神yù( ）于健全的 体格。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
